<body>
<div id="content" class="container">
    <header id="content-header">
<%
=begin      
        <div id="price-container">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-tag"></span><span class="price">$4.99</span>
        </div>
=end
%>        
        <%= image_tag('e-commerce2.png', id: "content-head-img", alt: "E-Commerce") %>
    </header>
    <section id="content-details" class="row clearfix">
        <article id="details-article" class="col-sm-8">
            <h1 id="article-title">E-Commerce <span class="font-weight-light"></span></h1>

            <h3><small>By <a href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#author-modal">Think Green.</a></small></h3>

            <br>
            <p>Nuestras zapatillas son basura y estamos orgullosos.</p>
            <br>

            <p>Aca tendrias que poner todo lo que queres comentar de lo que vas a vender, el porque de comprar las zapatillas reciclada y todo lo que se te ocurra.
            </p>
            <p><strong>Que Vendemos</strong></p>
            <ul class="no-indent">
                <li>Compromiso con el medio ambiente.</li>
                <li>Solucion al problema de la basura.</li>
                <li>Concientizacion.</li>
                <li>Algunas cosas mas.</li>
            </ul>
        </article>
        <aside id="details-aside" class="col-sm-4">
            <a id="btn-buy" href="receipt.html" class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart"></span>I want this!</a>
            <ul id="details-infobox" class="list-group">
              <li class="list-group-item active clearfix">DETAILS</li>
              <li class="list-group-item">You'll get one video</li>
              <li class="list-group-item clearfix">
                <span class="pull-left content-qualifier">Length</span>
                <span class="pull-right">30 minutes</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
        </aside>
    </section>
</div>
<%
=begin   
<footer id="site-footer">
Made by <a href="http://onemonth.com" target="_blank"><img id="one-month-footer-logo" src="img/one-month-logo.svg" alt="One Month"></a>
</footer>
=end 
%>
<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="author-modal">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h4 class="modal-title"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></span>Eco Shoes</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body clearfix">
            <div id="modal-left" class="pull-left">
                <p><strong>Descripcion</strong></p>
                <p>Como es el asunto de las zapatillas y quien las fabrica <a href="http://www.xinca.com.ar" target="_blank">Xinca</a> </p>
                <p>Why Think Green?
                  Let's talk about a minute of the importance of recycling and taking care about the envirnment.   
                </p>
                <p>Follow us on Twitter <a href="https://twitter.com/thinkgreen" target="_blank">@thinkgreen</a></p>
            </div>
            <div id="modal-right" class="pull-right">
                <%= image_tag('e-commerce2.png', alt: "E-Commerce") %>
            </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Scripts -->
<script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/lib/bootstrap.min.js"></script>